Generating a new password:
1) Choose length of password
2) Click on "Generate". A new random password will be generated.
3) Click on "Copy to Clipboard".

Encrypting the generated password:
1) Enter key name with ".key" extension. Eg: gmail.key
2) Click on "Generate key". A key will be generated to encrypt and decrpyt the password
3) Enter name of file where encrpyted password will be saved, with ".txt" extension. Eg: gmail.txt

Decrypting a password:
1) Enter key name of password to be encrypted.
2) Click on "load key"
3) Enter name of file to be decrypted next to encryption box
4) Click on "Decrypt". The original password will be visible
